    • com.lef.scanner中IBeaconConsumer的使用

      参数类型为IBeaconConsumer的com.lef.scanner中的方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      void IBeaconManager.bind(IBeaconConsumer consumer)
      绑定到服务或者Activity Binds an Android Activity or Service to the IBeaconService.
      boolean IBeaconManager.isBound(IBeaconConsumer consumer)
      判断是否应用是否绑定服务
      Tells you if the passed iBeacon consumer is bound to the service
      boolean IBeaconManager.setBackgroundMode(IBeaconConsumer consumer, boolean backgroundMode)
      设置蓝牙扫描模式为前台或后台，后台模式比较省电
      This method notifies the iBeacon service that the IBeaconConsumer is either moving to background mode or foreground mode When in background mode, BluetoothLE scans to look for iBeacons are executed less frequently in order to save battery life The specific scan rates for background and foreground operation are set by the defaults below, but may be customized.
      void IBeaconManager.unBind(IBeaconConsumer consumer)
      解绑定
      Unbinds an Android Activity or Service to the IBeaconService.
